2nd Level: Runic Warhammer
Summon a magical warhammer using Intelligence for attack and damage rolls.
At 6th level, gain an extra attack with this warhammer.
2nd Level: Runic Casting
Lose all spell slots; craft runes to cast spells instead.
Craft a number of runes equal to your Intelligence modifier during a long rest.
Crafting a rune requires an Arcana check; DC is 10 + (2 x spell level).
6th Level: Runic Plate Armor
Craft magical light armor with AC of 12 + Intelligence modifier.
Summon armor as a bonus action.
Use your reaction for resistance to a damage type, limited by Intelligence modifier.
10th Level: Efficient Crafting
Halve the time required to craft each rune.
Craft additional runes equal to half your Intelligence modifier during a long rest.
Once per long rest, reroll a failed crafting check.
